utions. Using\nSED modeling, we also demonstrate that the sample of z ~ 2 star-forming\ngalaxies observed by the MOSDEF survey is representative of the parent catalog\nof available such targets. We conclude that previous MOSDEF results on the\nevolution of star-forming galaxy emission-line properties were unbiased\nrelative to the parent z ~ 2 galaxy population.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Jun 2022 18:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 24 Aug 2022 20:13:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-09"}
