st energies), the cross-section of\nproton-air interactions has to be 800 mb at 140 TeV CM energy, accompanied by\nan increase of a factor of 2-3 in secondary particles. We also study the muon\nproduction of the showers in the same scenario.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Jun 2022 18:01:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 14 Jul 2022 14:25:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-15"}
