ulation. In addition, quiescent CO-driven activity may\naccount for the brightness of the comet in 2022 January to February, but that\nvariations in the cometary active area (i.e., the amount of sublimating ice)\nwith heliocentric distance are also possible.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Jun 2022 20:08:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-27"}
