ng attacks. We study potential vulnerabilities in\nthe perspective of physical layer authentication, network access security, and\ncross-layer authentication mechanisms. This study opens a new direction of\nresearch in the analysis and design of a security framework that can address\nthe unique challenges of coexistence networks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Jun 2022 03:12:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-01"}
