 significant\ndamping, to the extent that the waves would not be detectable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Jun 2022 08:09:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 Jul 2022 06:51:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-21"}
