ndata set to reproduce this research and to foster future RBA research. Our\nresults provide insights on selecting an optimized RBA configuration so that\nusers profit from RBA after just a few logins. The open data set enables\nresearchers to study, test, and improve RBA for widespread deployment in the\nwild.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Jun 2022 09:14:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 Nov 2022 09:16:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-11"}
