w scattering) mechanism,\nrespectively. An additional ferromagnetic contribution to anomalous Hall effect\n(AHE) for both ordinary and anisotropic components in Hall signal was\nregistered and attributed to the effect of magnetic polarization of 5d states\n(ferromagnetic nano-domains) in the conduction band of Ho0.8Lu0.2B12.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Jun 2022 11:57:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-01"}
