hich agrees with the notion that the mass\nweighted collision temperature of the C$_{2}^{-}$-He system defines the\ninternal rotational state population.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Jun 2022 13:47:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-31"}
